{"tid":1467682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣改革] 流言止於智者","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:36.000Z","uid":174541,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98e5abf2088d0083d79d37899cf05ff67cf816ab","tid":1467682,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"禮貌版<br />\n前線你好！核彈我也不會割。天琦說過與港共鬥爭不能有任何底線。既然有鬼捉不了已成事實(亦得到官方承認)，何不反其道而行，將一切大眾不能接受的行為推卸給popo(注意！並非割！)有了這免死金牌，前線能放下民意顧慮，盡情去做該做的事(不要斷正就可以)。你們的背後有我們！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誠狠版<br />\n屌你老母，醒少少好唔好?班差佬畀咗咁大 個核彈你都唔識玩?！ 天琦講過你班撚屌唔好有任何潔癖， 咁撚正氣點打中共啲陰招。示威肯定有鬼， 捉嚟都嘥鳩氣。 用下你個豬腦逆向思維咁諗， 有咩事咪奶撚落曬啲臥底到囉。 大眾淨係需要一個合理到嘅版本，陰謀論冇所謂㗎。 拎撚住依個免死金牌， 前線手足咪可以放手做，文宣我哋咪可以輕鬆打囉。 屌你老母，對面元朗嗰時已經做緊謠，唔係唔撚返佢哋呀?</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b51efa4e537666a1c1e910c5f686557fc8aed0c","tid":1467682,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7d405f8a65823be9a62dad1e9b89cce25901be","tid":1467682,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffc38281c4aa511ca7a6ce07e54e74f8f8d0e16","tid":1467682,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd46652e93a222e952b4162a1869ebcbb3e3983","tid":1467682,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" clas